# CredentialManager

The Credential Management in the library is built upon the Vault API.

It's initiated by passing along the Vault API key for the desired credentials list.

## Manager Creation

### API

```
from wcp_library.credentials.api import AsyncAPICredentialManager

CredentialsManager = AsyncAPICredentialManager(<API_KEY>)
```

### FTP/SFTP

```
from wcp_library.credentials.ftp import AsyncFTPCredentialManager

CredentialsManager = AsyncFTPCredentialManager(<API_KEY>)
```

### Internet

```
from wcp_library.credentials.internet import AsyncInternetCredentialManager

CredentialsManager = AsyncInternetCredentialManager(<API_KEY>)
```

### Oracle

```
from wcp_library.credentials.oracle import AsyncOracleCredentialManager

CredentialsManager = AsyncOracleCredentialManager(<API_KEY>)
```

### Postgres

```
from wcp_library.credentials.postgres import AsyncPostgresCredentialManager

